                     <interp inst="t18280410-207-person1174" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was at work with the prosecutrix; I went into the shop, and served the prisoner with nuts; I opened the till then, and saw some silver and farthings in it - he went out - I went into the room and sat down - we afterwards heard money jink twice; we went out, and I saw the prisoner behind the counter; 3s. 6d. was found under the mat; the farthings lay at a little distance; nobody came into the shop after him; he is a sweep.</p>
